      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then chop the<strong> green beans</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
