      "instruction": "<p>While the paneer is browning, top, tail and peel the <strong>mango<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p><p>Stand the mango<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> upright and very carefully slice the flesh away from the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Tip: If you feel resistance against your knife, it means you are hitting the stone</p><p>Dice the <strong>mango flesh</strong>, discarding the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
