    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the paneer is browned, return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with the <strong>tomato paste </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
