    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has slightly thickened, stir through the <strong>browned paneer</strong>, <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min further  – this is your <strong>creamy paneer & mango curry</strong></p>",
